                                        Our Products


                                            We offer Best Executions services for single orders, baskets and more sophisticated
                                            trades, and ensure secure and seamless Access to 50 exchanges worldwide.

                                            Structured Products

                                            Tailor-made structured solutions for equities, funds, hybrids or hidden assets Innovative
                                            structures for Equities, Funds and Hybrids to address investment needs of retail
                                            investors within local compliance / regulatory constraints and offer innovative
                                            investment alternatives to High Net Worth Individuals
                                        

                                            Flow & Financing products



Volatility Products: Listed/OTC Options, Volatility/Variance Swaps,
                                                    Options on Variance, Dispersion Strategies, Correlation strategies, etc.



Dividend products: Dividend Swaps, Options, Futures, Funds on Dividends,
                                                    etc.



Delta One Products: Convertible Bonds, Synthetic Convertible Bonds,
                                                    Certificates, Exchange Traded Funds (ETFs), Equity Swaps, Performance Swaps, Synthetic
                                                    positions, etc.



Financing Products: Securities Lending & borrowing(SLAB) and Synthetic
                                                    SLAB, Contract for Differences (CFDs), Prime Brokerage.



                                            Strategic Equity

                                            Bespoke value added equity-based solutions for Corporates.
                                            
                                            Comprehensive suite of product ideas arising from a broad-based approach and our
                                            capacity to handle tax, accounting and legal isuues.
                                        

Main Activities: 




                                                    To optimise balance sheets, provide equity financing solutions, monetise and hedge
                                                    large equity shareholdings



                                                    To structure, hedge and implement compensation & benefit programs such as the ESOP
                                                    plans



                                            Harewood Asset Management

                                            A 100% BNP Paribas subsidiary, regulated and registered by the Autorité des Marchés
                                            Financiers
                                            
                                            Innovative investment solutions by leveraging BNP Paribas CIB expertise
                                            
                                            Three investment universes: systematic strategies, structured strategies and alternative
                                            investments
                                        

















