 About the Group
 


 Activities
 


Activities BNP Paribas organizes its businesses into two main fields of activity: Retail Banking & Services (RBS) and Corporate Institutional Banking (CIB). 
















Our businesses







Retail Banking & Services
Our network of retail banks and specialized financial services located around the world.DISCOVER






Corporate & Institutional Banking
A wide range of financial solutions available for our Corporate & Institutional Banking customers.DISCOVER




















