BNP Paribas | Products








































We deliver responsible consumer finance solutions.







Home
Our Solutions





In this fast changing, digital first world we understand that customer expectations around choice and experience is key to your business success. We will work with you to deliver responsible consumer finance solutions that help you increase your sales, attract new and retain existing customers and increase your customer loyalty. Together, we truly become Partners in Growth.



This is how we'll work with you...


Understand your requirements

We take time to understand your business and your customers needs.


                            View Flexible Finance Case Study
                            




Create the right solutions

We work with you to create the right solutions for your business.


                            View IHG Case Study
                            




Turn insight into value

Generate value from your customer data and our industry insights.


                            View Flexible Finance Case Study
                            







Our Solutions







Retail Finance
We can help your customers spread the cost of larger purchases through our simple, easy to use finance solutions. Our multi-channel systems, accessed in store or at home, are quick to integrate and offer comprehensive reporting. With a seamless customer journey enabled by a secure online account management system your customers remain in control of their spending.












Cards
We can create credit card programmes to help your customers get value from their everyday spending so you can increase customer loyalty, footfall and repeat sales. We can also give valuable insights about your customer behaviours to create a more personalised, effective approach to your marketing.  









Premium Finance
We can help your customers budget and finance insurance premiums with easy and convenient affordable monthly payments, helping you to generate more sales.  









Personal Loans
We can partner with you to design tailor made business models enabling you to create value, revenue and deepen relationships with your customers.  We bring product development and cross sell expertise to provide a range of straightforward, responsible loans.
















BNP Paribas to buy out full stake in Italian insurance unit from Ageas | Reuters
























































































