Structured Products at BNP Paribas Wealth Management

Nathalie Osphare-Druilhe








Since the wave of financial crises' in the late 2000s, structured products have persistently adapted to an increasingly demanding economic, legal, regulatory and fiscal environment. Yet at the same time, these sophisticated products have maintained a prime position in the portfolios of investors who have the requisite knowledge and investment profile. 

 At BNP Paribas Wealth Management, we design and create bespoke structured products to meet the requirements of a discerning clientele who seek original solutions to standard financial investments. The unique strengths of our structured products offer the advantages of capital protection, an enhanced risk/return profile and more. 

Watch this video to learn more from our expert Nathalie Osphare-Druilhe, Head of Structured Products and Derivatives.


















